OL,3,CPeople urged to report any anti-social
OL,4,Cbehaviour so police can pinpoint
OL,5,Cproblem
OL,7,FPeople in south Wales are being urged
OL,8,Fto report any cases of anti-social
OL,9,Fbehaviour (ASB) as the police try and
OL,10,Ffind new solutions to crack down on
OL,11,Fthis type of crime.
OL,13,FSouth Wales Police is launching its
OL,14,F'Project Pinpoint' campaign, which it
OL,15,Fhopes will allow them to gather data
OL,16,Fon ASB regarding how and where it is
OL,17,Fhappening.
OL,19,FThe force then aims to use the data to
OL,20,Ffind targeted solutions with the
OL,21,Fcommunity to help tackle the problem.
