OL,7,FSouth Wales Police say the project
OL,8,F'aims to tackle ASB head-on, through
OL,9,Fpositive engagement, while fostering
OL,10,Fstronger connections within the
OL,11,Fcommunity.'
OL,13,FIt says its targeted approach has had
OL,14,Fsuccess in Bridgend following a spate
OL,15,Fof ASB at a carpark in the town.
