OL,7,FThe force says the site had become a
OL,8,Fhotspot for ASB and using data it
OL,9,Fobtained from people reporting the
OL,10,Fissue, they were able to pinpoint
OL,11,Fmultiple car parks across Bridgend,
OL,12,Fwhere the issue was happening.
OL,14,FThis then led to Sergeant Dan Parry
OL,15,Ffrom South Wales Police to reach out
OL,16,Fto the Ospreys Rugby Club to help try
OL,17,Fand combat the issue.
