OL,7,FThe organisation, along with Bridgend
OL,8,FYouth Support and South Wales Police
OL,9,Fwere able to develop an initiative for
OL,10,Fyoung people to play touch rugby in
OL,11,Furban areas like car parks.
OL,13,FThe 'TACKLE After Dark' project is
OL,14,Fsaid to have helped result in a 66%
OL,15,Fdecline in ASB reports in Bridgend.
OL,17,FSgt Parry said: "This initiative
OL,18,Fdemonstrates the importance of
OL,19,Freporting anti-social behaviour.
