OL,7,F"Within the first five weeks of the
OL,8,Fproject with TACKLE after Dark, they
OL,9,Fengaged with 107 individuals. In six
OL,10,Fmonths, reports of anti-social
OL,11,Fbehaviour in Bridgend dropped, from
OL,12,F172 reported calls to 57 reported
OL,13,Fcalls.
OL,15,F"Every report made really does count."
