OL,7,FSouth Wales Police & Crime
OL,8,FCommissioner Emma Wools said: "We have
OL,9,Fbeen extremely successful in our bids
OL,10,Fto the Home Office Safer Streets Fund
OL,11,Fand the allocation of #1million
OL,12,Ftowards community safety initiatives
OL,13,Fis an endorsement of the strong
OL,14,Fpartnership working we have in South
OL,15,FWales.
OL,17,F"We have worked closely with local
OL,18,Fauthorities and other partners to
OL,19,Fidentify the drivers of local problems
OL,20,Fand how best to tackle them together.
