OL,7,F"We can achieve far more by working
OL,8,Ftogether which is why it is so
OL,9,Fimportant for those who are
OL,10,Fexperiencing anti-social behaviour to
OL,11,Freport these issues so we can focus
OL,12,Four efforts and resources where they
OL,13,Fare needed most.
OL,15,F"Project Pinpoint, which is funded by
OL,16,FSafer Streets, aims to raise awareness
OL,17,Fof the importance of reporting anti-
OL,18,Fsocial behaviour so we can make a
OL,19,Fpositive difference and make our
OL,20,Fcommunities safer for everyone."
